Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:40.36,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊擁抱 心靈的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.51,0:00:46.72,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱情燃燒 創造奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:52.09,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣受著傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:58.32,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相發誓過的 遙遠的銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.05,0:01:04.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座的幻想 只有夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:10.60,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也奪不走 因為是心靈的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:16.54,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 少年都是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:20.72,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 明天的勇士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.46,0:01:28.18,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 就像天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:35.84,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士星矢 現在就展開羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:35.01,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣字幕组&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.72,0:00:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當邪惡在此世蔓延之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會現身的希望之戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身著星座之聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆發蘊藏在身體中的能量「小宇宙」進行著戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們正是 保護大地上愛與和平的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷落到暗之遺跡的光牙 阿莉雅 伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人嘗試著逃離這裡的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.01,0:01:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗的利刃正悄悄逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅途的終焉！少女的光芒與年輕的戰士們！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.48,0:02:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…罪孽？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是 難道你認為自己是純潔無垢的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了成為世界的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像天使般被撫養長大的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了提升你的光之力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小到大你一直被美好的事物所環繞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後 你就唯命是從 使用這力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你所做的 全都是為了將世界導向滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.50,0:02:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你想要阻止痛苦在世上不斷蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但製造出這痛苦的根源 正是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的存在給很多人造成了傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已知曉自身的罪孽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界原本就是黑暗的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.53,0:03:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過於強大的光明 只會招致不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 陷入內心的黑暗吧 永遠的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮吧 我想你一定會喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…阿莉雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想看到你戴上它的笑容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 你將成為統治世界的王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為保護新的雅典娜的強大聖鬥士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是對我的懲罰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了達成雙親的期待…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能守護得了阿莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能守護真正重要之人的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光之小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能被黑暗所吞噬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的光明是罪孽深重的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒發現它只會招致災禍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為自己所犯下的罪孽 可以被諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道將來還會用這種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯下何種罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我只要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要還有人需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要還有生命會為我的光芒而喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就…我就想成為光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為照亮黑暗的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.88,0:06:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有考慮到你真正的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.91,0:06:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都對我很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的小宇宙居然是暗屬性…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 燃燒你的黑暗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 你就能變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強到足以打敗瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能打敗瑪爾斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯 我決饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打倒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 讓你真正的力量覺醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙 不可以燃燒暗之小宇宙！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光之子啊 絕不把暗之子交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許將光牙拉入黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正的小宇宙是暗屬性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以來放出的光芒又是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是沙織小姐的光之小宇宙在保護著你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但並不僅僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.87,0:08:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 正因為你相信著自己心中的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能燃燒起光之小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 一起破壞暗之核心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到這件事的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從莎爾娜小姐那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻斷了瑪爾斯與星矢那場戰鬥的隕石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那時分別走上兩條截然不同的命運之路的嬰兒的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 好像就是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗之小宇宙水晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不能令它恢復黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光之天馬決不可以墮落成為暗之天馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 你一定不會被黑暗吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 還有我在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪爾斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光之小宇宙 多麼美麗的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等的就是這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准你繼續利用阿莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會繼續為你所用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的光之力量決不會再為你所用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旅途中 我懂得了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活在這世間的生命 還有人們心中的美麗與溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要守護這美麗的世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說這世界美麗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說這充斥著慾望 妒忌 仇恨 背叛的世界美麗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我要守護她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的光芒 分分秒秒照耀著她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.04,0:12:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的光芒嗎 蠢到極致
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的光芒是為了照耀我所創造的新世界才存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 快回來 回到我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你嗎 天馬座的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決不會把阿莉雅交給你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我們要守護她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區青銅又能有什麼作為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:13:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢再不會來救你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼強大的暗之小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次遇到這麼強大的小宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廬山升龍霸！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.01,0:13:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白狼拳 傳神無雙！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼獅轟炸！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鷹旋翔掠殺！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬流星拳！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 吾之光芒喲 回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我再也不會回到你身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要保護
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界和生命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 請借給我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠驅散那黑暗的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙的水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了阿莉雅的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.80,0:15:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那光輝閃耀的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是 雅典娜的光芒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雅典娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於作為雅典娜覺醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅 成為了雅典娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.79,0:15:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 新的雅典娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的力量來創造理想的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事 才不會讓你得逞 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會如你所願 瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅的光芒是雅典娜的光芒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼保護這光明 便是我們的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士？別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就墮入黑暗中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要光的力量還在支持我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 成為黑暗中的塵埃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要雅典娜的光芒仍在閃耀 我們就能戰勝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬流星拳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的拳頭竟然擊中了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你膽敢反抗我嗎 阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的傢伙 你本來是可以成為新世界的雅典娜的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅 阿莉雅 阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅 阿莉雅 阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙 都平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜 我能遇見你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼摩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍峰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都對我那麼溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙 我已經不用再回到瑪爾斯身邊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 大家卻一定要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.49,0:21:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去阻止瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護這世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去 沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉雅 阿莉雅 阿莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們帶給我幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.83,0:21:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:21:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.83,0:22:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.58,0:22:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有聖鬥士最強實力的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身著閃耀著黃金光輝的聖衣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.37,0:22:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揮出光速之拳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.57,0:22:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護著掌管黃道星座的十二宮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.25,0:22:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們正是黃金聖鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.09,0:22:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 年輕的聖鬥士的戰鬥將衝進新的篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 聖鬥士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.89,0:22:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最強軍團！黃金聖鬥士集結！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:23:08.85,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集，終於進入新章
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:23:08.85,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖鬥士們的熱血戰鬥去往黃金十二宮
